'''1979年NBA选秀'''（{{lang|en|1979 NBA draft}}）是美国[[国家篮球协会|国家篮球协会]]第33次年度[[NBA选秀|选秀]]。本次选秀于1979年6月25日举办。在这次选秀中，22支NBA球队轮流从美国大学业余篮球运动员和其他包括国际球员在内的适格球员中选拔队员。前两个选秀顺位属于各联盟排名垫底的球队，先后顺序则由投掷硬币来决定。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/draft_evolution.html|title=Evolution of the Draft and Lottery|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-10-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100927173723/http://www.nba.com/history/draft_evolution.html|archivedate=2010-09-27|deadurl=yes}}</ref>[[洛杉矶湖人|洛杉矶湖人]]在一次交易中获得了来自[[犹他爵士|新奥尔良爵士]]的首轮选秀权，在投掷硬币中取胜，获得了[[NBA选秀状元列表|第一顺位]]，[[芝加哥公牛|芝加哥公牛]]则获得了第二顺位。首轮其他顺位及其他轮数的选秀顺序根据前一赛季中各队的胜负记录逆序分配。完成了四年大学的球员可以参与选秀。如果一位球员提前离开大学，那么他必须等到所在年级到达毕业年份后方有资格入选。在选秀之前，共有5名大学低年级生根据“困难”规则被认定有资格参加选秀。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/news/lottery02_earlyentry_history.html|title=Early Entry Candidate History|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090914112043/http://www.nba.com/news/lottery02_earlyentry_history.html|archive-date=2009-09-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>这些球员向联盟提交了申请并提供证据证明自己存在经济困难，联盟据此认定他们可以更早开始其职业生涯，以赚钱糊口。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/players/haywood_bio.html|title=Spencer Haywood Bio|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-10-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101119165820/http://www.nba.com/history/players/haywood_bio.html|archivedate=2010-11-19|deadurl=no}}</ref>在选秀开始之前，爵士从[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]搬到了[[盐湖城|盐湖城]]，更名为[[犹他爵士|犹他爵士]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/this_date_june.html|title=This Date in History–June|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-10-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101119022331/http://www.nba.com/history/this_date_june.html|archivedate=2010-11-19|deadurl=yes}}</ref>选秀共计10轮，有202名球员参加。
== 选秀球员概述 ==
来自[[密歇根州立大学|密歇根州立大学]]二年级学生的[[魔术师约翰逊|魔术师约翰逊]]依照“困难”条款加入选秀，并被洛杉矶湖人在第一顺位选中，成为首位大学低年级生状元秀。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8HoRAAAAIBAJ&sjid=kukDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2515,1070550|title=Olajuwon should go first in today's draft|date=1984-06-19|newspaper=Gainesville Sun|location=Gainesville, Florida|publisher=The New York Times Company|accessdate=2010-10-28}}</ref>之后，在其新秀赛季，他随湖人出战赢得[[NBA總冠軍列表|NBA总冠军]]。他同时也赢得了[[NBA总决赛最有价值球员|NBA总决赛最有价值球员]]，成为首位获得此殊荣的新秀球员。他13年球员生涯均在湖人度过，共获得5个NBA总冠军。他同时三次摘得[[NBA最有价值球员|NBA最有价值球员]]和总决赛最有价值球员，10年连续入选[[NBA最佳阵容|NBA最佳阵容]]，12年入选全明星赛阵容。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/players/johnsonm_bio.html|title=Magic Johnson Bio|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-10-21|archive-date=2016-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120190843/http://www.nba.com/history/players/johnsonm_bio.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于其杰出成就，他被列入[[奈史密斯篮球名人纪念堂|奈史密斯篮球名人纪念堂]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/awards/hof.html|title=Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame Inductees|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|date=|accessdate=2010-10-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100913063921/http://www.basketball-reference.com/awards/hof.html|archivedate=2010-09-13|deadurl=no}}</ref>在1996年联盟庆祝50周年之际，他被列入[[NBA50大巨星|NBA50大巨星]]名单当中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/history/50greatest.html|title=The NBA's 50 Greatest Players|work=NBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-10-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100918202136/http://www.nba.com/history/50greatest.html|archivedate=2010-09-18|deadurl=yes}}</ref>在退役之后，约翰逊曾在{{nbay|1993|end}}短暂出任湖人的过渡时期主教练。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/johnsma02c.html|title=Magic Johnson Coaching Record|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-10-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100925023639/http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/johnsma02c.html|archivedate=2010-09-25|deadurl=no}}</ref>

第5顺位[[西德尼·蒙克利夫|西德尼·蒙克利夫]]赢得过2次[[NBA年度最佳防守球员|NBA年度最佳防守球员]]，连续5年入选All-NBA Teams、[[NBA最佳防守陣容|NBA最佳防守陣容]]和全明星赛。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/m/moncrsi01.html|title=Sidney Moncrief Statistics|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-10-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100922182232/http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/m/moncrsi01.html|archivedate=2010-09-22|deadurl=no}}</ref>第12顺位[[小吉姆·帕克森|小吉姆·帕克森]]曾入选All-NBA Team，2次入选全明星赛。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/p/paxsoji02.html|title=Jim Paxson Statistics|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-10-22|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111050848/https://www.basketball-reference.com/players/p/paxsoji02.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>第3顺位[[比尔·卡特赖特|比尔·卡特赖特]]，{{nbay|1990|end}}到{{nbay|1992|end}}随[[芝加哥公牛|芝加哥公牛]]连续三次获得NBA总冠军。他同时也在新秀赛季入选过全明星阵容。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/c/cartwbi01.html|title=Bill Cartwright Statistics|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-10-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100927055311/http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/c/cartwbi01.html|archivedate=2010-09-27|deadurl=no}}</ref>之后他曾担任过三个赛季的公牛队总教练。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/cartwbi01c.html|title=Bill Cartwright Coaching Record|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-10-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100906231751/http://www.basketball-reference.com/coaches/cartwbi01c.html|archivedate=2010-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>第65顺位[[比尔·兰比尔|比尔·兰比尔]]在{{nbay|1988|end}}到{{nbay|1989|end}}随[[底特律活塞|底特律活塞]]获得两个NBA总冠军，并4次入选NBA全明星赛。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/l/laimbbi01.html|title=Bill Laimbeer Statistics|work=basketball-reference.com|publisher=Sports Reference LLC|accessdate=2010-10-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100925041355/http://www.basketball-reference.com/players/l/laimbbi01.html|archivedate=2010-09-25|deadurl=no}}</ref>在退役之后，他曾执教[[WNBA|WNBA]][[Detroit_Shock|Detroit Shock]]8个赛季，带领球队在2003、2006和2008年三夺WNBA总冠军。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wnba.com/coachfile/bill_laimbeer/index.html|title=Bill Laimbeer Bio|work=WNBA.com|publisher=Turner Sports Interactive, Inc|accessdate=2010-10-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111012013811/http://www.wnba.com/coachfile/bill_laimbeer/index.html|archivedate=2011-10-12}}</ref>

